stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_init: receive block B
    q_init --> q_iter: txs = B.transactions, i = 0
    q_iter --> q_check: i < len(txs)
    q_iter --> q_valid: i >= len(txs)
    q_check --> q_invalid: txs[i].gasLimit > 16777216
    q_check --> q_next: txs[i].gasLimit <= 16777216
    q_next --> q_iter: i = i + 1
    q_invalid --> [*]: reject block B as invalid
    q_valid --> [*]: accept block B (gas cap check passed)
